  "name": "RPlog_A_New_Beginning",
  "title": "A New Beginning",
  "summary": "On a landing platform of the city-moon Nar Shaddaa, the tattooed ex-military spacer Esmeraldas -- 'Ezzi' -- disembarks from one ship and crosses paths with the smuggler Jaspar Andromidas as he offloads a cargo of delicate chak root from his Ghtroc freighter Hirakiis. Striking up a conversation in search of a drink and work, Ezzi reveals herself as a former Cloud City Air Defense Guard and shipyard mechanic, and Jaspar -- impressed by her technical knowledge and her knack for handling rough crowds -- hires her on the spot as engineer. The two share drinks at the notorious Meltdown Cafe, where Ezzi stares down the suspicious regulars and trades shop talk about modifying his ship while staying on the right side of the law. Jaspar then gives her a tour of the Hirakiis, where she diagnoses its dated but sound systems and suggests upgrades, and the scene ends with her settling in for the night as a new member of his crew.",
